CHAT.comment: Freeplay. Mother and Child sit on living+room floor playing with a box of experimenter provided toys. They play with a Snoopy clock with removeable numbers , a tea set , and giant Lego blocks. Child's speech is fairly intelligible.

u.a: takes plastic container from box of toys .
starts to put clock in plastic bag .
tries to give bag to Child .
opens new container with tea set .
takes sip and holds it up to Child .
holds pieces up to show Mother .
